<br />

<br />
The last patch made us happy because it fixed some minor bugs with /melody, but more importantly, it gave us back our ability to taunt mobs with a certain selection of single-target dots (our chant line).
<br />

<br />
If you can handle it, I think that swarm kiting is by far the most fun way to kite in the game.  The learning curve may be steep, but the rewards are great.  To tell you the truth, I never AE kited till long after I dinged 65.</span></td>
